			<title>Division and Fractions</title>

	  	<objectives>
		<ul>
	  		<li>
	  			<p>
				Develop the fundamental property of fractions by understanding them as pieces of a whole.
	  			</p>
	  		</li>
	  		<li>
	  			<p>
	  			Develop a geometric meaning of <m>\frac{a}{b}</m> when <m>b</m> is not a whole number.
	  			</p>
	  		</li>
			<li>
				<p>
				Work with units of measurement via multiplying and dividing fractions.
				</p>
			</li>
			<li>
